<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>For You</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #111;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

.section {
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20px;
}

button {
  padding: 12px 25px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  border: none;
  background: white;
  color: black;
  font-size: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

.hidden {
  display: none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- SECTION 1 -->
<div class="section">
  <h1>Hey :)</h1>
  <p>Don’t scroll too fast</p>
  <button onclick="showSection(1)">Proceed</button>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 -->
<div class="section hidden" id="s1">
  <h2>So you actually clicked...</h2>
  <p>Not surprising. You're always curious.</p>
  <button onclick="showSection(2)">Continue</button>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 -->
<div class="section hidden" id="s2">
  <h2>Top 5 reasons you're annoying:</h2>
  <p>1. You overthink everything</p>
  <p>2. You never listen</p>
  <p>3. You disappear randomly</p>
  <p>4. You act strong but you're soft</p>
  <p>5. You became important to me</p>
  <button onclick="showSection(3)">One more thing</button>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 4 -->
<div class="section hidden" id="s3">
  <h2>We’ve had chaos...</h2>
  <p>Random talks. Stupid fights.</p>
  <p>But somehow you stayed.</p>
  <button onclick="showSection(4)">Final message</button>
</div>

<!-- FINAL -->
<div class="section hidden" id="s4">
  <h1>Happy Friendship Anniversary ❤️</h1>
  <p>You genuinely matter to me.</p>
  <p>I hope one thing stays constant — us.</p>
  <p>You’re stuck with me now :)</p>
</div>

<script>
function showSection(n) {
  document.getElementById("s" + (n-1)).style.display = "none";
  document.getElementById("s" + n).style.display = "flex";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
